rows.label: qst201801_0010
rows.name: Would you look at that!

rows.label: qst201801_0020
rows.name:
There's a bunch of 'em...
Maybe we should come again later.

rows.label: qst201801_0030
rows.name:
It may be wise...
Otherwise the hunters may become the fodder...

rows.label: qst201801_0040
rows.name: It's fine!

rows.label: qst201801_0050
rows.name:
No need to worry.
I'll talk to 'em, I'm sure they'll listen to reason!

rows.label: qst201801_0060
rows.name:
I mean, you say "sure," but...
You've not exactly got a great track record, you know?

rows.label: qst201801_0070
rows.name:
Come on, every fox has its day!
Isn't that right, Uka?

rows.label: qst201801_0080
rows.name:
Very right!
You can leave this to me!

rows.label: qst201801_0090
rows.name:
Ooh, don't be afraid.
Auntie Uka is your friend!

rows.label: qst201801_0100
rows.name:
Now... Mind telling me
where your leader is?

rows.label: qst201801_0110
rows.name: Ah! Gotcha!

rows.label: qst201801_0115
rows.name: Um, could I please have a moment of your time...?

rows.label: qst201801_0120
rows.name: We've just come to rescue some of our friends.

rows.label: qst201801_0130
rows.name:
They're little Phonexes, a bit smaller than you,
and super-super cute.

rows.label: qst201801_0140
rows.name:
They mustered all their courage to come here!
Does that ring any bells?

rows.label: qst201801_0150
rows.name: No, not "food"! "PHO-NEX"!

rows.label: qst201801_0160
rows.name: D'you think she's getting through at all?

rows.label: qst201801_0170
rows.name:
Who can tell...?
Seems to be upsetting them if I'm honest...

rows.label: qst201801_0180
rows.name: Oh, so you're gonna play dumb, huh?

rows.label: qst201801_0190
rows.name:
Well, you are not fooling me!
Give back the Phonexes, right now!

rows.label: qst201801_0200
rows.name:
Ohhh, come onnnn!
Why won't you listennn?!

rows.label: qst201801_0210
rows.name:
Uka, it's no use!
Get out of there!

rows.label: qst201801_0220
rows.name: Aaaaaah!

rows.label: qst201801_0230
rows.name: Uka! Are you okay?

rows.label: qst201801_0240
rows.name:
I was just trying to talk!
That really flipping hurt!

rows.label: qst201801_0250
rows.name:
What's the harm in a little talking?
Why's it always fight-fight-fight with you...

rows.label: qst201801_0260
rows.name: Just talk to me, darn you!!

rows.label: qst201801_0270
rows.name:
There! Tit for tat!
Now we're even, see?

rows.label: qst201801_0280
rows.name:
That sounds like...
failure to communicate, doesn't it?

rows.label: qst201801_0290
rows.name:
Indeed. Unfortunately, it seems
we're not getting out of this without a fight...

rows.label: qst201801_0300
rows.name: Onwards!
